{"TopicId":205995,"ForumId":38,"TopicTitle":"Change the rules of this game!","CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-12-15T20:21:51Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-12-15T20:21:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWill this be chaotic?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut will be interesting?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHopefully.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe idea of this game is that whenever you do not like the rules. You can simply add or remove or change a rule.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is a few SOLID rules that cannot be changed\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. No rules that make this a spam game or an unplayable game\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Try to avoid making a rule that makes this a clone of another game (like don\u0027t make this a number war)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. Do not make a rule that seems to annoy people (like don\u0027t make\u00A0 a rule that you have to ping a random person, that kinda fits into rule 1)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4. Obviously, follow forum rules\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n5. Do not prevent others from playing this game (ex: Username cannot change rules or make rules or play a round,) likewise, don\u0027t make rules that undo the latest rule unless it has to be done to keep the game flowing or there isn\u0027t an example of how that rule should be played out\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOK here are the CURRENT rules of the game (ping me if it changes)\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E1. Make one big word\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E2. Change all the vowels to \u003Cstrong\u003Eone \u003C/strong\u003Evowel\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E3\u00A0. \u00A0Add -raptor to the end of your new word to make a dinosaur name\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E4. Add a family line to the name (ex: Saparmarkatsaurus the Third or III)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003EHOW to modify the rules\u003C/b\u003E:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFeel free to copy and paste this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ERULE CHANGE:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ENEW RULE/END RULE/CHANGE RULE: INSERT RULE HERE\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n@The Doodling Astronaut , rules have changed\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:24px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cu\u003EYou do not have to change the rules if you don\u0027t want to. You can continue playing the game that is already set\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:24px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cem\u003ELets see how this expirement goes...\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRound 1:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like food -\u0026gt; I Liki Fiid\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-01-01T15:30:52Z\u0022 title=\u002201/01/2022 03:30  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 1, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by The D